Shifted in at start and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L on turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Began well from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, 1/2L back on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Away well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, angled out early in straight, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 lengths or so back, saved ground throughout, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 6, raced towards rear on the outside, 3 lengths or so back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well, raced prominently but 3 wide, 3/4L back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Inconvenienced at start, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Slow away, at back along the fence, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Eased to sit just behind the leaders, 2 wide, made early move 600M, led 300M, overhauled 100M.
Eased to obtain box seat, closed off well 200M.
Eased back, 2-4 wide, dashed well 250M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, dashed well 200M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, lack room 300M, just held ground.
Pushed to take rail and lead, out of fuel 300M, post-race vet exam did not show any significant findings.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, lack turn of foot.
In front of midfield, no progress in straight, post-race vet exam did not show any significant findings.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, made early move 1000M into the lead, weakened 200M, post-race vet exam did not show any significant findings.
Eased at start to take cover at back, lack room 5-3, dashed fairly, post-race vet exam did not show any significant findings.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, made early move 900M, emptied 300M.
Raced in midfield, along the rail initially, shifted out after passing the 900M, ran on nicely and held off late challenge to win by a neck.
At rear, 2 wide, closed of strongly to be in a close finish with the winner.
At rear, along the rail, showed strong dash in the last 100M for 3rd.
Raced in behind midfield, wide no cover after 550M, made ground and closed off strongly for 4th.
Raced prominently, 2 wide, just weakened in the last 25M.
Raced in midfield initially, sent forward after 800M, 2 wide, one paced only in the Straight.
Raced in midfield initially, pressed forward and took lead after 550M, weakened after passing 50M.
Raced in behind midfield, wide no cover, pretty one paced.
Raced in front of midfield initially, dropped back after 450M, 2 wide, nothing in the Straight.
Sent forward and took lead, along the rail, did not feature in the Straight.
At rear, 3 wide with cover after 600M, nothing in the Straight.
Sent forward, dropped off after 500M and eased down in the Straight.

Raced just worse than midfield away from rail before moving three wide at 750m & improving around runners to third position near 600m. Dashed well to move to lead at 250m before drawing away in final furlong to win strongly.

Pushed forward to race second away from the rail. Moved up to share lead entering the last section, joined quickly by winner soon after straightening, fought on ok to hold second in final stages but was no match for winner.

Raced just worse than midfield on rail. Moved away from inside near the 800m, eased wider at the 400m when travelling strongly & 4L form the lead before closing off well in the final stages to well beaten third. Better.

Raced prominent to lead in first furlong before being crossed & racing in midfield away from rail. Entered last section under 3L behind, moved three wide soon after before finishing off only steadily to hold 4th, beaten 3.5L.

Drifted back after the start & raced second last for the majority. Continued rearward entering last section when over 5L from the lead before closing off ok from the back to be midfield, beaten a similar margin on line.

Ridden early before getting nice run 1,1 throughout. Straightened only 2L from lead but failed to challenge in straight & weakened out in last furlong to be well beaten in midfield. Travelled keenly & wouldn't relax  rider.
Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Stayed close to the rail on cornering when about 3L from the lead before weakening out in the straight to be beaten over 6L.

Drifted back after start & was left racing three wide no cover near the back. Moved slightly closer passing 700m, continued wide around final bend before giving a few lengths to be beaten 6.5L. Rider questioned, see report.

Drifted back after the start & raced at the rear throughout. Moved wide but with cover at the 650m, very wide on cornering when a long way from lead before passing a few but still finishing a fair way behind winner.
Had a soft run on leaders back throughout. Was under 2L from the lead on straightening before weakening poorly in the straight to be well beaten.
Slow away & raced near the tail throughout. Was 5.5L from lead entering last section & failed to improve in straight. Second last nearly 8L behind on line.
Improved after the start assume the lead after 300m. Emptied soon after cornering & weakened badly in last furlong to be last.
Began smartly from a wide draw, raced prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, kept on very well in straight, won by 3/4L.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced prominently on the inside, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, same position on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, very wide turning in, made good progress in the run home, no threat to the first few.
Crowded shortly after start, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, brushed the rail near 850M, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Jumped well from gate 11, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, very wide into straight, made minor progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, made minor progress early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Moderately away from the widest gate, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
Travelled just in front of midfield, along the rail, ran on smartly to the line, won by 1L.
Rolled forward, took box-seat, kept finding to the line but was no threat to winner.
Jumped only fairly, in worse than midfield, 2 wide, improved steadily to the line to take 3rd.
Urged along, just behind midfield early but wide, only found cover after taken to the rear, swung widest on exit, saved ground and hit the line fairly.
Bumped start, raced front of midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced to the line.
Raced at the tail, along the rail, dashed on a little late.
Niggled along early, settled towards the rear, wide with cover, saved no ground.
Bumped start, in worse than midfield, along the rail, failed to kick on from 150M out.
Asked early, settled outside lead 1L behind, faded passing 200M. (See Incident Report)
Forward, took rail and led, headed and faded at 200M. (See Incident Report)
In midfield, wide and no cover, wasn't in it.

Drifted back before picking up swiftly on the rail to be 2L back in 5th into back straight, gained 4th 700M out and further closer in 3rd home bend, quickened well to take charge inside 200M, won comfortably.
Hampered at the start, settled towards the rear in 10th on the rail, steady headway from 700M to be 2L 6th rounding home bend, tightened for a run 200M out, fought on steadily without threatening.

Began well, gradually settled some 3L back in 6th, inconvenienced briefly rounding home bend and soon shaken up, went very wide into straight but quickened well under pressure inside final 150 metres to snatch 3rd late.
Soon came to join the leaders, gradually shifted back from the 850 metres to one-out-one-back position, came under pressure in straight to hold place chance only to be pipped for 3rd late.
Taken back from a wide gate and waited with, commenced move on the rail passing the 600 metres and saved ground turning in, fought on under pressure despite a difficult ride.

Gradually taken back to rear of midfield in 8th from a wide gate travelling wide throughout, drifted further back to 10th 700 metres out, baulked for a run over 200 metres out, fought on steadily closing stages.

Bumped after starting from a wide gate, soon moved up to join the leaders 4-wide turning into back straight, ridden positively to dispute lead 2-wide from the 700 metres, found no extra inside final 120 metres.
Taken back from the widest gate, remained well back and trailed the field rounding home bend, did not find much room inside final 200 metres and not able to be properly tested.
Crowded at start losing ground, towards the rear and travelled keenly most of the way, kept on same pace without making any serious impression in the run to the line.

Jumped best and ridden along to share early pace 3-wide, gradually taken back for cover from the 800 metres but in vain, in 5th about 2L off the pace rounding home bend, faded steadily under pressure after straightening.
Shared early pace on the rail, gained half a length advantage from the 600 metres, joined by others again entering home straight, folded up quickly after straightening.
With leaders early stages, gradually drifted back to midfield in back straight, widest runner turning for home after travelling wide most of the way, made no further impression.
Crossed to the lead passing 1000M, set steady pace in middle stages, continued on well when asked top of straight and comfortably held off pursuing rivals final 200M.
Reserved in midfield along the fence, took a while to get going on straightening, did best work final 200M to go 2nd close home.
Always well placed behind leaders in a slow run race, tried hard on straightening but couldn't quite close the gap on winner, lost 2nd near line.
Settled midfield, 5th going into final turn, driven out 450M, put in a mild bid in the run home, just missed a minor placing.
Began awkwardly, held up towards the rear in a slow run race, responded well final 300M to claim 5th near line.
Jumped on terms, settled down behind midfield, bustled along 500M, stayed on moderately to the line, finished just behind 2nd and 3rd in a blanket finish.
Quickest away, restrained to sit behind leaders along the 2-path, fought on one paced in the straight, faded late and lost several places.
Taken back for cover, held up at the rear 7Ls off the pace in a slow run race, closed off final 400M fastest but left with too much to do.
Slowly away from draw 12, dropped back to race at the rear as opposed to obtaining a forward position, brought widest top of straight, ran on without troubling leaders.
Not hurried, settled towards the rear 5-6Ls back, gave limited response on straightening, never involved.
Travelled strongly when racing wide down the back straight early stages, improved from 900M to race outside leader but inclined to lay out, hung on to 200M then weakened away.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled towards the rear along the inside, couldn't go on passing 300M. Never dangerous.
Began fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, 6 lengths back, 2 wide from 700M, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to score by a head.

Clean jump, raced prominently on the inside before being crossed and checked near 1000M, 2 lengths back in the middle stages, angled out 450M, hit the front 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Began smartly from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, closed off well to take a place.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 400M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, found rail near 1000M, led by 3/4L on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back to race at tail, 9 lengths or so back, still 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home to be nearest on line.
Began well from the widest draw, raced in midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer after passing 800M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, made minor progress early in straight, no extra final 100M. (Lost right hind plate near 800M.)
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)

Moderately away, raced better than midfield on the outside, moved closer after entering the back straight, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 700M, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Began awkwardly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to make any progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight to score.
Began awkwardly and made contact, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take 2nd, always held.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, finished off well to take a place.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared 300M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, made minor progress thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, angled out 550M, same margin back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, carried wider after passing 550M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, blocked after passing 200M, cleared 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, no clear run 300M, cleared after passing 200M, kept on evenly thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at rear on the outside, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Bumped start, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Inconvenienced at start, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Out in line, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Eased back, 2 wide, lack room 4-2, dashed strongly when clear.
Pushed to take rail and lead, hung on well until last few strides overhauled.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2-4 wide, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, 2 wide, just held ground.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide, held ground in straight.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, blocked most straight, dashed strongly.
Hard ridden early but not muster, midfield, 2 wide, blocked most straight, dashed well.
Slow away, pushed to obtain a midfield spot on the rails, raced keenly, lack room in straight, just held ground.
Very slow away, at back along the fence, blocked most straight, dashed well.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, emptied 200M, post-race vet exam did not show any significant findings.
Eased at start, trapped 2-4 wide, dashed well 300M, run ended 100M, post-race vet exam did not show any significant findings.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, blocked whole straight, not tested.
Sent forward, along the rail, kept on going to win the race.
Settled to race in midfield, 2 wide, ran on strongly in the straight.
At rear, 2 wide, showed strong dash in the last 150M.
Settled in midfield, 2 wide, near the 300M held up for clear running, after that made ground steadily and finished okay for 4th.
At rear, 2 wide, made ground and ran on to the line.
Raced behind the lead, along the rail, weakened after passing 150M.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, found no extra approaching 150M.
Sent forward and took lead, 2 wide, emptied after passing 250M.
Taken back and raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide but with cover, no progress in the Straight.
Raced prominently, 2 wide, nothing in the Straight. (Roarer)
Raced in midfield, wide no cover, lost ground in the Straight.
Slow to begin and raced at rear, along the rail, did not improve in the straight.

Had a nice run in midfield between runners, eased wider on cornering, dashed up to lead at 250m, held lead without bursting away, got tired in final stages & just had enough in the tank to hold out late closer.
Steadied & taken back to second last away from rail. Moved very wide when about 6L behind on straightening before flying home in the final stages to fall be a SHD behind on line.
Drifted back to last after the start. Continue at the back nearly 7L behind on straightening before making up very good late ground to move to third late beaten only a neck on line.
Steadied & then drifted back after start before improving position to midfield along the rail in middle stages. Shifted outwards at the 350m mark before closing off steadily to hold 4th.
Raced in midfield before being checked away from heels near the 850m. Entered last section just under 4L from the lead before finishing off steadily to be beaten under 2L in midfield.
Had a nice run in midfield away from rail throughout. Under 2L form the lead on straightening but finished off only very one paced & held similar margin on line. Close behind.
Race din midfield but was trapped racing three deep without cover for the majority. Continued to finish off steadily & wasn't beaten far in midfield.
Held early lead before being headed & racing on leaders back from 900m. Moved over the heel dos two leaders just before straightening, peaked on effort mid-straight, not beaten far in midfield.

Steadied from outside gate & got back to 4th last away from rail. Ridden along before straightening, entered last section 5.5L from lead before finishing off one paced when hanging inwards in straight. Not ridden out late.

Was ridden along after start to hold position in midfield away from rail. Raced slightly wide but with cover in middle stages, shifted to be widest runner on straightening before finishing off only one paced without threatening.
Raced in midfield along rail throughout. Continued to be only just over a length form the lead at the 200m mark before being over-run in late stages when giving ground.

Pushed forward form wide gat, raced three wide outside leaders before two wide from the 900m. Moved to narrow outright lead entering last section, joined passing the 300m before weakening out in last furlong.
Had no speed & drifted back to third last along rail. Was hard ridden from the 600m, entered last section over 6L from the lead & made no headway. Well beaten.
Didn't begin fast but improved position under hard riding to dash between runners and take the lead near the 950m. Headed soon after straightening & weakened out badly to be last. Lame post-race.
Commenced well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, 2 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden from 300M, finished off strongly to score by a narrow margin.

Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden after passing 400M, finished off strongly, led close home but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Bumped start and unbalanced, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well in the middle stages, hard ridden approaching 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two close home.
Away well, positioned a length behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden 350M, finished off well without threatening.
Shifted out at start, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands' rail, hard ridden from 350M, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from gate 1, raced towards rear in the middle of the track, 3 to 4 lengths back, made good progress final 400M without threatening.
Slightly hampered shortly after start, positioned a length behind the leader, 3 away from the stands' rail, cleared 300M, finished off evenly.
Out with rest, raced towards rear, 2 away from the stands' rail, made good progress final 400M without threatening. (Lost left front plate on jumping.)
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the middle track, hard ridden 400M, only showed limited response, ran on evenly thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced towards rear on the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 400M, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced prominently, hard ridden from 250M, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader, 2 away from the stands' rail, bumped 400M, peaked 300M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands' side, crowded 400M, weakened thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)
Sent forward to take lead, on rail, led all the way to win by 1-1/4L.
Rolled forward, assumed box-seat when entering back straight, kept pushing but took no ground off the winner, finished 2nd 1-1/4L behind.
Raced just behind midfield, 2 wide, made nice ground and continued on nicely to the line.
Niggled along, box-seat early but slotted a pair back at 1200M, showed dashes before flattening.
Travelled in about midfield, wide until 1000M, keen in the middle stages, was one paced only.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, improved slightly then closed off late.
Jumped awkward, worked forward to sit outside lead, faded gradually in the straight.
Settled to race in about midfield, along the rail, showed dashes early before finishing one-paced.
Began only fairly, sat towards the rear and on rail, didn't make ground.
Took back, raced at the rear, on rail, did not improve.
Jumped only fairly, took back to be at rear, 2 wide, saved no ground.
Settled to race one-out one-back, no kick and run ended at 200M. (Blood in trachea and see Incident Report)
Slotted into midfield, 2 wide, pressured 650M out, wasn't in it.
At rear, wide and no cover from 1000M, never a factor.
Settled well behind, last and widest runner into straight, switched in for a run passing the 250 metres, ran on strongly to prevail by a narrow margin. (Tactic in home straight questioned)

Soon dropped well behind, pulled forward in the slow pace on home bend, checked off heels at about the 800 metres dropping to last few, baulked for a run in straight until quickening well between runners inside final 100 metres.
Broke well from the widest gate, gradually taken back to rear of midfield but remained wide without cover throughout, gained slightly closer to 2L 5th into straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.

Began well from a wide gate, gradually taken back to midfield closer to rails coming onto home bend, travelled keenly in the slow pace, fought on well inside final 300 metres to hold every chance and narrowly miss a placing.
Ridden forward to join the leaders, disputed lead most of the way until swamped for a placing final strides.
Broke well from the one draw to hold slender lead and set a slow pace, fought on under pressure in straight but swamped for a placing final strides.
Settled just better than midfield in 5th within 3L of the slow pace, saved ground on the rail rounding home bend but could find no clear run the length of the straight, not tested.
Soon dropped towards rear, travelled wide and keenly in the slow pace rounding home bend, fought on steadily under pressure down the centre of the straight.

Moderate start from a wide gate and soon dropped well behind, pulled forward in the slow pace 4-wide without cover rounding home bend, one of the widest turning in , unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Began awkwardly, travelled keenly one back in 3rd on the rail, in similar box-seat position into home straight, baulked for a run most of the way to the line, not tested.
Settled one-out-one-back, held every chance early in straight but unable to sustain effort inside final 150 metres.

Not far off from leaders early stages, left racing 3-wide without cover from 900M, moved up to chase leaders home turn, produced a sustained effort from 400M to reel in the long-time leader close home.
Began fairly, moved up to take the lead passing 1200M, set good pace to straight, continued on strongly from 400M only to be caught by winner close home. Well clear from rest.
Reserved towards the rear, 6Ls to make up 400M, stayed on moderately to claim a non-threatening 3rd, well behind first 2.
Held up behind midfield 3-wide, 5Ls off the pace halfway, put in a mild bid leaving home turn, got up for distant 4th late.
From draw 1 settled in midfield along the fence, responded fairly turning in, never able to challenge first 2, briefly went 3rd 150M, edged out to 5th late.
Went forward to take early lead, tracked leader from 1100M, under pressure 500M, battled on to hold 3rd until 150M then faded away final stages.
Stumbled at the start, held up behind midfield along the fence, kept on same pace turning home, never troubled leaders final 300M.
Became fractious as the start was effected, slowly away, settled towards the rear on inside, couldn't go on passing 400M, never reached contention.
Taken back from wide draw, settled at the rear 8Ls off the pace, driven wide home turn, failed to run on.
Caught wide early, strode forward to chase leader passing 1100M, found disappointingly little when placed under pressure 600M, out of contention 250M. (Jockey unable to offer any explanation.)
Dropped back to a rearward spot, raced 3-wide throughout, driven 600m out but made no real progress. Never in the picture.
Lost ground at the start, caught 4-wide no cover in midfield, bustled along 600M but failed to quicken, never able to challenge.
Restrained to race behind midfield, failed to respond when driven out nearing 450M, never involved.
Chased leaders early stages, travelled keenly, under pressure prior to home turn, soon gave ground and finished tailed out. (Jockey unable to offer explanation for the performance.)

Taken back from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 1000M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared after passing 300M, finished off strongly to score.
Out in line, trapped wide in midfield early, sent forward after passing 1200M, raced in 2nd in the middle stages, no cover throughout, kept on very well in straight to take a place.

Stumbled on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, carried wider after passing 700M, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home to take 3rd.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L, kept on well until final 100M, peaked and headed 50M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the outside, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Stumbled at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield early, 3 wide from 1050M, moved closer on turn, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Away with them, chased leader, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 800M, 2 lengths back turning in, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide better than midfield early, travelled keenly near 1100M, 3 wide from 700M, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from gate 8, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, made no progress thereafter.
Made contact shortly after start, raced towards rear on the outside, 5 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, angled out after passing 550M, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths back, same position on turn, angled out 500M, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact shortly after start, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, hit the front 250M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, similar position on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Began very awkwardly and bumped, raced behind midfield on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made minor progress early in straight, no clear run near 200M, weakened final 100M.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced in midfield on the inside, moved closer along the rail on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 250M, weakened final 100M.
Jumped well, raced prominently but 3 wide, a length back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Away with them, positioned 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, angled out 500M, peaked early in straight, inconvenienced near 300M, weakened thereafter.

Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, briefly headed after passing 500M, retook the lead early in straight, kept on well to the line, won by a narrow margin.
Away well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, took the lead near 500M, headed early in straight, kept on well to the line, always held.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide behind midfield, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, finished off well to take a place.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, closed off well without threatening.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 7 lengths back on turn, made good progress early in straight, no clear run final 50M.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 100M, made minor progress thereafter.
Average to begin, trapped wide in midfield early, moved a bit closer after passing 700M, 3 wide with no cover on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 200M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Settled one off one back, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Slow away, at rear, lack room 4-2, dashed strongly when clear.
Box seat, held ground for 3rd.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, ran on until 100M weakened.
Midfield along the fence, lack room 4-2, dashed well.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, raced keenly, just held ground.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, ran on ok.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, made early move around the field in 4 wide from 700M, run ended 250M.
Pushed to take rail and lead, out of fuel 250M, post-race vet exam did not show any significant findings.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, in the straight made ground and closed off strongly to score.
Raced behind the leader, along the rail, ran on gamely but couldn't hold off the winner.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, made ground and close off strongly for 3rd.
Sent forward, 2 wide, kept up and stayed on well to the line.
Raced in behind midfield, 3 wide but with cover, made some ground in the Straight only.
Sent forward, along the rail, weakened after 150M.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, only one paced.
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, pretty one paced.
At rear, 2 wide, showed no turn on foot after 100M.
Raced in front of midfield, wide no cover, eased down after passing 200M. (See incident report)
At rear, along the rail, never a factor. (See incident report)
Raced detached and at rear, did not feature.

Raced three wide no cover on speed before improving to be outside the leader, 2 wide from the 550m. Moved to narrow lead at 250m, continued to hold narrow advantage all the way to line to win by a nose.
Drifted back to race third last away from rail. Got clear running on straightening when continuing rearward before closing off very strongly to miss my only a nose on the line.
Raced second at the leaders quarters before being crossed & racing 1,1 from the 550m mark. Closed well all the way to the line & was only beaten half a length.
Raced on the leaders back throughout. Stayed close the rail in the straight, awkward near 150m before closing well to be beaten under a length.
Raced in midfield away from the rail. Eased wider passing 400m, wide in straight, closed off well in late stages to be beaten just over 1L.
Drifted back to rail near the rear throughout. Stayed close to the inside in the straight, closed off steadily to only be beaten 2L in midfield.
Steadied at first bend & taken back to the tail. Was a clear last on straightening before closing off strongly in final 100m before being hampered for room & not ridden out when closing off late.
Began fast to lead. Headed by winner near the 250m mark & weakened out in last furlong to be well beaten.
Raced in midfield along the rail. Moved off the rail on straightening but finished off only one paced in the straight, not beaten far but was second last.
Raced three wide with cover when just worse than midfield before being left without cover from the 500m. Forced very wide on cornering before failing to finish off. Last.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move approaching 400M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover after passing 600M, moved closer on turn, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 75M.
Clean jump, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide turning in, closed off well to take a place.
Began well, raced prominently on the inside early, allowed rival to cross near 650M, sat right behind the leader on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, 8 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight.
Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, found rail near 600M, travelled well on turn, hit the front 300M, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 150M.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made minor progress.
Inconvenienced at start, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, similar position on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, moved a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted in abruptly at start and made contact, raced prominently on the outside, led by 1/2L on turn, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final furlong.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Travelled in behind midfield, 2 wide, great run to chase down leader, ran home strongly to win by 1/2L.
Rolled forward, took box-seat, kicked on ear-ly before weakening late, just held onto 2nd.
Raced towards the rear, wide but with cover, made ground and closed off gamely to take 3rd.
Jumped awkward, took back, made 600M turn 2 wide, improved and ran on fairly.
Raced towards the rear initially, drifted out to improve at 800M, continued one paced.
Asked early, took rail and led, weakened about 150M out.
Worked forward, settled one-out one-back, improved from 800M, stayed on until about 150M.
Travelled in midfield, along the rail, saved no ground. (See Incident Report)
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, never threaten.
Niggled along, shared lead 2 wide, showed nothing. (See Incident Report)
In midfield, 2 wide, never a factor.
Took back, towards rear initially, worked forward to be midfield, wide throughout how-ever, found nothing.

Ridden forward from wide gate before settling back in midfield in 6th, got closer to 3L off the pace 900M, commenced move 400M and wide into straight, hit the front 150M to win readily despite hampered 250M out.

Pressed forward from widest gate before settling wide in 7th in rear of midfield, raced keenly in the slow pace early in back straight, commenced move home bend and wide into straight, nearest at finish.

Well there early, settled about 3L off the pace in 3rd, became closer in 4th when pace slackened 800 meters out, held every chance early in straight but unable to sustain effort inside final 100 metres.
Settled in midfield on the rail, angled out for a run entering home straight, finished off the race well inside final 100 metres.

Close up on the rail early, drifted back to midfield passing the winning post the first time, became 5th 1200M out and further closer to pace 900M out, went wide turning for home, one-paced in straight.
Lacked pace and dropped towards rear despite niggled along, fought on under pressure in straight without threatening.
Settled towards rear, wide under pressure rounding home bend and widest runner into straight, made up some late ground.
Travelled freely in first few, obtained one back position in 2nd rounding first bend, became 3rd when pace slackened 800 metres out, soon faded after straightening.

Niggled along early to be 4th on the rail, switched off rails 1200M out and made headway 3-wide in back straight to reach 2nd 800M out, came under pressure rounding home bend and weakened in straight.
Took up running 3-wide passing the winning post the first time, obtained rails run in front rounding first bend, led until headed and folded up quickly inside final 250 metres.
Ridden early before settling wide in last few, travelled one from last after first bend, saved ground on the inside turning into home straight, unable to quicken under pressure.
Settled in last, niggled along in back straight, tailed-off turning for home.
Away well, always close up behind leaders, picked up pace passing 300M down the outside, led near 100M winning in fine style.
Driven along and crossed to the lead near 800M, continued on well turning in, caught by winner 100M out, held on for 2nd.
Slow to begin from draw 10, shifted across behind runners, 4-5Ls off the pace home turn, finished off well to go 3rd close home.
Raced keenly early stages when pace was low, caught wide no cover before improving to race outsider the lead after 800M, fought on steadily in the straight, lost 3rd late stages.
From draw 1 obtained a midfield spot along the fence, kept on evenly turning for home but never finding the pace to challenge leaders.
Guided to a 2-wide spot in midfield 3-4Ls back, driven nearing 400M, ran home fairly, always held by leaders.
Held up behind mid-division, caught 3-wide no cover from 800M, brought wide home, stayed on without threatening leaders.
Bumped by rival at the start, taken back to race in the rear, responded fairly when driven out top of straight, never a threat to leaders.
Jumped well but soon shuffled back to a position behind midfield, couldn't muster the pace to challenge on straightening, never dangerous.
Up with early pace, tracked leaders entering back straight, fought on to 200M then weakened rapidly to finish last.
Inconvenienced at start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on strongly in straight, easily scored.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths back, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, closer on turn, very wide into straight, made very good progress in the run home, nearest on line.
Moderately away, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, kept on well early straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began smartly from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Hampered start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, moved a bit closer after passing 450M, very wide turning in, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 9, raced behind midfield on the inside, 6 lengths back, 2 wide turning in, one-paced in straight.
Bumped start, race 2 wide in midfield, commenced move approaching 450M, 3 to 4 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn but still the last into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the inside, peaked 400M, weakened early in straight.

Placing: PU
Comment: Shifted in at start and made contact, trapped very wide, a length or so back, weakened after passing 1000M, soon pulled up. (See Racing Incidents.)

Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground to turn, angled out approaching 500M, hard ridden 350M, hit the front 200M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Moderately away, raced in 2nd, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, challenged the leader 600M, took the lead early in straight, headed 200M, kept on well to take 2nd.
Taken back to race at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back in the middle stages, 3 lengths back on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest finish.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 wide turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened final 50M.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, challenged by rival from 600M, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the outside, carried wider 500M, made no progress in straight.
Eased to sit in front of midfield along the rails, lack room 400M, progressed steadily when clear.
Eased to sit in midfield, progressed steadily 400M.
Behind midfield, on the fence, blocked most straight, closed off strongly when clear.
Eased to sit behind the front runners, ran on well to the line.
At rear, along the fence, lack room in straight, made steady ground.
Slow away, took rail at rear, progressed steadily in straight, lack room 200M.
At rear, trapped 3-4 wide, made ground 300M.
Hard ridden to cross in front and obtain box seat, out of fuel 200M.
Hard ridden early, trapped 3-4 wide in midfield, made ground 400M, run ended 150M.
Pushed to take rail and lead, weakened 200M.
Slow away, at rear, 2 wide, ran on fairly.
Slow away, at rear, no progress.
Pushed early, failed to muster, trapped 3-4 wide behind midfield, no progress, post-race vet exam did not show any significant findings.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3-4 wide, dropped off 450M, post-race vet exam did not show any significant findings.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, showed strong dash in the last 200M to win by 3/4L.
Settled to race in midfield, 2 wide after 850M, ran on strongly in the straight.
Raced behind the lead, along the rail, unable to obtain clear running until the last 150M, showed strong dash thereafter for 3rd.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, stayed on but weakened after passing the 50M. (See incident report)
Sent forward and took lead, along the rail, weakened after passing the 50M.
At rear, along the rail, improved steadily to the line.
At rear, 2 wide, only one paced in the Straight.
Sent forward and raced next to the lead, 2 wide, lost ground in the last 75M.
Pushed forward from gate 12, raced second at the leaders hind-quarters in middle stages. Moved to lead soon after straightening, dashed clear to win very easily. Impressive.

Drifted back & raced third last away from the rail. Steadied away from heels near 850m. Continued rearward on straightening, shifted ground near 200m before closing strongly to move to well beaten second in final stages.

Caught 4 wide in midfield after start before improving position & racing three wide no cover outside leaders from 800m. Continued wide on bend, couldn't sprint with winner passing 300m, fought on well, caught for 2nd late.
Raced three wide with cover in midfield for the majority. Moved to second place passing 250m mark, battled away ok but was caught for a minor placing late. Improved run.
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Peaked on effort near the 200m, gave a length or two to be well beaten in midfield.
Didn't begin fast but mustered speed to improve along the rail & race just behind the leading trio along the rail. Finished off fairly when racing greenly to be in midfield, 2L behind second.
Improved after the start to race in midfield between runners. Shifted outwards at 350m when about 3L behind before finishing off only fairly in final furlong. Well beaten in midfield.

Commenced awkwardly & bumped and consequently got back near the rear after start. Steadied at 950m & taken back to clear last. Straightened 5.5L from lead, stayed along rail before finishing ok to midfield in final stages.

Raced just worse than midfield along the rail throughout. Was 4 lengths from the lead on straightening, moved away from rail soon after but failed to challenge & weakened in late stages to be well beaten.

Was trapped racing 4 wide in midfield but with cover before being left in that position but without cover from about the 800m. Continued wide around bend, straightened under 4L behind but weakened out after wide passage.
Raced three wide with cover in midfield before being steadied & drifting slightly further back near the 700m. Straightened about 5L from the lead before weakening to be long third last.
Pushed forward to lead. Joined by winner approaching the 300m mark before weakening out quickly in last furlong.

Bumped after the start & drifted back towards the rear. Hung outwards & lost ground around the 800m bend before losing further ground & relegated to last near 600m. Weakened further in straight to finish a long last.
Began well, positioned 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Shifted out on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Commenced well, tracked leaders but 3 wide early, 2 wide on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.

Shifted out abruptly at start, unable to slot in, trapped very wide, a length or so back, bumped 1000M, took the lead 850M, led by 1/2L on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared 200M, made good progress thereafter to be nearest on line.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made some headway in straight.

Bumped start, raced prominently on the inside early, allowed rival to cross near 800M, sat right behind the leader on turn, not enough room early in straight, cleared 250M, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail, 5 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide from 600M, very wide into straight, one-paced in the run home.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, bumped near 1000M, headed 850M, found rail near 800M, 1/2L back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Bled.)
Jumped well, raced better than midfield on the outside, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, unable to slot in, trapped very wide slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slotted into midfield, wide but with cover, kicked away 250M out, ran home a comfortable winner.
Couldn't muster, found cover at rear but wide, made ground and closed off nicely, just no match to winner.
Eased to find cover, in worse than midfield, 2 wide, no daylight until 250M, ran home fairly.
Eased back, raced at the rear, remained away from the rail, switched across heels 300M, closed off okay thereafter.
In midfield, remained one off the rail, slightly held near 400M, kicked on until flattened in final furlong.
Sat just behind midfield, 3 wide with cover, ran on okay.
Hard ridden early, was prominent but wide and no cover, flattened passing 150M.
Rolled forward, took box-seat, kept up till about 150M only.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2 wide, was one paced and weakened.
Bumped start, forward to take rail and led, emptied near 250M.
In worse than midfield, wide but with cover, never a factor.
Jumped awkward, rolled forward to sit outside lead, gave ground in straight. (See Incident Report)
Sat just front of midfield, on rail, weakened near 250M. (See Incident Report)
Bumped start, in midfield, wide and no cover from 1100M, run ended on straightening. (See Incident Report)
Behind midfield in joint 9th on the rails, saved ground on the inside turning for home, ran on well inside final 250 metres to claim victory close to home.
Jumped fairly but soon recovered along the rails to join the leaders, took up running 800 metres out, kicked 2L clear over 200 metes out and flattered, caught close to home.
Lost ground at the start settling in last few, obtained a clear run over 200 metres out, finished off the race well.
Settled in midfield on the rails, came to challenge after straightening, fought on under pressure inside final 250 metres to be nearest at finish.
Settled behind midfield in joint 9th, switched out for a run entering home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled slightly worse than midfield, soon came to challenge under pressure after straightening, unable to sustain effort and lost placing inside final 120 metres.

Jumped awkwardly from the widest gate, wide with leaders early before taken back from the 1050 metres, some 4L back in 6th coming onto home bend, remained wide turning in, fought on until finding no extra inside the 100 metres.
Began well but soon taken back, some 4L back in 5th rounding home bend, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Settled some 3L back in 4th on the rails, found nothing under pressure in home straight.
Settled in last few from a wide gate, never seen with a chance.
Soon taken back from a wide gate, trailed the field from rounding home bend and widest runner turning into straight, made no further impression.

Soon ridden to lead, obtained 2-wide position coming onto home bend and headed inside the 800 metres, came under pressure from a similar position into straight, folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Broke well to share early pace, shifted one back to 3rd passing the 1000 metres, weakened under pressure after straightening.
Taken back from wide draw, reserved near the rear 10Ls back, moved up well on inside rounding home turn, soon quickened to lead passing 350M, kicked clear and maintained a strong gallop to the line.
Tracked leaders on inside, fought well passing 500M on the rain affected ground, no match for winner over final 250M but kept on steadily to hold 2nd spot comfortably.
Shifted across behind runners, held up at the back about 10s off the pace, niggled along from 800M, widest into straight, found less than expected, ran on to claim non-threatening 3rd.
Settled behind mid-division, 6Ls off the pace halfway, wide into straight, stayed on without threatening.
Held up behind midfield, 7-8Ls back on settling, under pressure 600M out but failed to quicken, ran home only fairly, never a threat to leaders.
Strode forward, moved up to the lead near 1200M, steadied the pace middle stages, headed inside 350M, soon faded out of contention.
Held up towards the rear, shuffled back to last making the turn for home, gave limited response on straightening, never threatened.
Led early stages before taking a trailing spot behind leader from 1200M, no extra passing 300M, weakened towards the line.
Caught wide early stages, 3rd on settling chasing leaders, came under pressure 600M, soon gave ground and finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)

Placing: PU
Comment: Chased leaders early stages, went amiss at 850M and was retired from the race. (Left hind fetlock injury.)

Began smartly, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, not enough room early in straight, squeezed through gap inside final furlong, hit the front 100M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Away well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, moved a bit closer on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Began well, trapped very wide in midfield, moved closer on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Clean jump, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, showed good response early in straight, hit the front 200M, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped the inside gate on jumping, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight.
Shifted out at start, sent forward to take the lead, found rail approaching 900M, led by 1/2L on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 550M, bumped 500M, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Fast into stride, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, cleared 200M, only showed limited response, eased final 50M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Inconvenienced at start, raced at rear on the outside, carried wider 550M, bumped and unbalanced 500M, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, same position on turn, failed to make any progress in straight, eased final 150M.
Inconvenienced at start, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, moved closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.

Bumped on jumping, raced towards rear on the outside, commenced move after passing 550M, made very good progress in straight, took the lead approaching 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, kept on same pace to the line.
Moderately away, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Lifted front feet on jumping, positioned a length behind the leader, travelled well to turn, ridden after passing 300M, challenged the leader 200M, peaked 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 12, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, 2 wide on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened final 100M.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, made some headway early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths or so back, crowded near 900M, same margin back on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2 lengths or so back, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rival on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened 300M, eased final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced 2 to 3 wide towards rear, found rail near 650M, 7 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the outside, 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, weakened early in straight.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield early, commenced move after entering the back straight, took the lead 850M, led by 5 lengths on turn, kept on very well in straight, easily scored.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 8 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly to take a place.
Bumped start, raced towards rear on the outside, 9 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Slightly slow out, raced in midfield on the inside, 7 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide in mid-division, no cover for the majority of the race, 6 lengths back on turn, made minor progress early in straight, no extra final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, 6 lengths back turning in, one-paced in the run home.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 850M, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Taken back from gate 8, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Average to begin, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, 9 lengths back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began well, trapped 3 wide, a length or so back, 2 wide after passing 1500M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight. (Bled.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Eased to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Pushed early but not muster, at back on the rails, made early move 700M, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, on the fence, made ground 200M.
Pushed to take rail and lead, ran on until 100M weakened.
At back, 2 wide, made ground 200M.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide, ran on ok, post-race vet exam did not show any significant findings.
Slow away, at back, no dash, post-race vet exam did not show any significant findings.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, 2 wide, emptied 400M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, never improved.
Settled in midfield, wide no cover, kept on going to scored by a neck.
Raced behind the leader after 1050M, along the rail, stayed on but only headed in the last 30M.
At rear, 2 wide, swung widest on Straightening, showed strong dash in the Straight and finished 3rd.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide but with cover, ran on strongly in the last 50M.
Sent forward and took lead, along the rail after 1050M, weakened only in the last 50M.
At rear, along the rail, made minor ground in the Straight.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, only one paced.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, only weakened in the last 50M.
At rear from a wide barrier, 3 wide but with cover, one paced only.
At rear, 2 wide, did not feature in the Straight.
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, not competitive.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, lost ground in the Straight. Unacceptable performance. Must trial (See incident report)
Raced just worse than midfield away from rail. Ridden along passing 600m, wider on bend before closing strongly in the final furlong to steal advantage away from the leader in final stages.
Pushed forward to lead. Raced over a length clear soon after straightening, held lead until caught by fast finishing winner in final stages.

Threw head at the start & lost a length, raced last early before third last along rail from 500m. Shifted wider & bumped on straightening before making significant late ground down the outside to snare third late.

Had a nice run in midfield away from rail throughout. Eased wider on cornering, closed off steadily in the straight before shifting in near the 100 mark when moving to 4th place in later stages. Rider suspended  see report.
Crowded & lost ground at start before improving along rail to race in midfield. Stayed close to the rail in the straight & finished off evenly to midfield without threatening.

Ridden forward from outside gate to improve & race outside lead for the majority. Continued in second but dropped over a length from the lead entering last section before weakening a couple of lengths in final stages.

Trapped racing three wide without cover just behind the leading pair. Continued not far behind mid-straight before being hampered & losing rightful running at the 100m mark but looked beaten at that stage.

Hampered at start before racing worse than midfield along rail. Moved away from the rail passing 400m, wider on straightening, shifted back inwards mid-straight before racing in restricted room until inside final 75m.

Bumped & badly hampered at start before racing rearward away from the rail. Shifted very wide approaching bend, bumped on straightening when continuing at the back before finishing off only moderately down the outside.

Steadied & shifted rearwards after start before being relegated to last near 700m when continuing to be restrained. Stayed close to rail on straightening, shifted out mid-straight before closing evenly under no riding late.
Had a nice run 1,1 throughout. Peaked on effort mid-straight, raced tight between runners near 100m mark before weakening out in final stages to be second last.
Had a nice run on leaders back throughout. Weakened out in the straight & was last.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide behind midfield, bumped near 600M, commenced move 400M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced in midfield on the outside, there to turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.

Taken back from a wide draw, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed good response in straight, hit the front near 125M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two late.
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to make frame, nearest on line.

Jumped well from gate 11, trapped very wide, a length or so back, moved a bit closer 650M, raced 3 wide outside leaders on turn, kept on well early in straight, hit the front 200M, peaked and headed 125M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved round on turn, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, shared lead on turn, bumped early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, angled out 350M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (Lost right front plate in the middle stages.)
Clean jump, raced in mid-division on the outside, gradually dropped position in the middle stages, 6 lengths back turning in, passed a few beaten rivals in straight.
Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, bumped 300M, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, made contact near 600M, 4 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Sent forward, assumed lead outright by 600M turn, continued on nicely to win by 3/4L.
Jumped well, shared lead before easing to be in box-seat, switched to centre track in straight, kicked on to finish 2nd.
Began awkwardly, sat in front of midfield, on rail, ran on well for 3rd.
Settled in midfield, along the rail, ran on fair-ly to the line.
Raced in advance of midfield, 2 wide, ran on okay until flattened near 100M.
Slow to jump, at tail and made turns 2 wide, improved steadily on the outside.
Hard ridden, settled in midfield only, 2 wide, was one paced.
Niggled along, prominent but trapped wide, emptied passing 200M.
Raced towards the rear, on rail, kept going until weakened in the last 100M.
Awkward start, in worse than midfield, 2 wide, didn't improve.
Jumped awkward, at rear, 3 wide at turns, hampered 150M, wasn't picking up anyway.
Jumped well before easing into midfield, wide with cover, never in it.
Began well from the one draw, gradually taken back off the pace settling over 3L back in 4th, saved ground turning in for home, quickened well to hit the front over 150 metres out to win readily.
Amongst leaders early, gradually settled one back in 3rd inside the 900 metres, drifted some 3L back when pace quickened rounding home bend, hit the front briefly over 200 metres out but soon headed.
Soon dropped to tail-end, commenced move rounding home bend, switched out widest entering home straight, ran on well down stands side to be nearest at finish.

Recovered quickly from moderate start, gradually shifted back to 5th some 4L back passing the 900 metres, renewed pressure home bend and wide into straight, fought on under pressure but found no extra inside final 50 metres.
Close up early, carried over 4L back to 6th passing the 900 metres, drifted over 6L back when pace quickened onto home bend, forced to switch in for a run inside 250 metres, fought on steadily.
Settled mainly in midfield, came under pressure rounding home bend, fought on steadily down the centre of the straight without threatening.
Broke well but soon dropped behind midfield on the rail, fought on nicely without threatening.
Settled worse than midfield, dropped further back passing the 600 metres, fought on nicely in straight without threatening. (Lame)
Moderate start from the widest gate settling wide without cover towards rear, swung very wide into straight, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Crowded at start, settled well behind, saved ground turning for home but made no impression in straight.
Hard ridden from moderate start to take up running 1000 metres out and obtained rails run shortly after, quickened up the pace coming onto home bend, found no extra inside final 300 metres.
Ridden from a wide gate to be up with the pace, disputed lead 2-wide from the 850 metres, quickened with race leader coming onto home bend, dropped away quickly inside final 200 metres.
From draw 12 drifted back to race at the rear 6-7Ls behind leader, waited with on inside, finished off strongly passing 300M, got up near 50M to score his 6th win in the season.
Obtained outright lead passing 1400M, kept on well when placed under pressure early straight, caught by winner near 50M, held on for 2nd.
Shifted across behind runners for cover, settled towards the rear, raced keenly middle stages, closed off well passing 400M, just held by first 2 late.
Jumped on terms, settled down midfield along the fence, driven near 400M, stayed on moderately to line, held by first 3 at the finish
Never far off the pace, 5th on settling, swung to center of track leaving home turn, stayed in contention for a minor placing until no extra late stages.
Restrained to race at the rear, 7Ls off the pace on settling, made limited progress on straightening, always held by leaders.
Settled towards the rear 5-6Ls off the pace, swung wide into straight, stayed on fairly to line, never a threat to leaders.
Began only fairly from draw 1, recovered to track leader on inside, not quickened when pushed along 450M, no threat 200M from home, dropped away.
Tracked leader on outside, bustled along 600m to keep up with the pace, no extra 250M, weakened away.
Restrained in midfield 2-wide, travelled keenly in middle stages, failed to respond passing 300M, never reached contention. (Blood in trachea.)
Stumbled at the start, from draw 11 raced wide no cover chasing the leaders, came under pressure 500M, soon gave ground.
Obtained a 3-wide spot in midfield, struggled to keep up home turn, already beaten turning into straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide after passing 500M, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider after passing 500M, closed off well to take 2nd.
Slowly away, raced at rear, 8 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off well to make frame.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 125M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, there to turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Began awkwardly, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved round on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened final 100M.

Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, showed limited response early in straight, no clear run and inconvenienced near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced in midfield on the outside early, dropped towards rear after passing 1000M, 8 lengths back on turn, one-paced in the run home.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 3 wide behind midfield, there to turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Moderately away from gate 11, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, found rail near 550m, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
